WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
[Court]

2
00:00:00.678 --> 00:00:08.578
[Ambient sound]

3
00:00:01.175 --> 00:00:04.823
Zhang Peizan: I came back from walking the horses that day. Just when I walked to the garden,

4
00:00:06.475 --> 00:00:10.443
I heard the young lady and her fiancé talking.

5
00:00:08.578 --> 00:00:09.128
[Opera orchestra plays]

6
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:14.775
She asked him to come to the garden in the middle of the night to get gold.

7
00:00:15.588 --> 00:00:16.278
[Sound effect: Gasp]

8
00:00:15.625 --> 00:00:17.600
Feelings of greed stirred in my heart at that moment.

9
00:00:16.278 --> 00:00:18.178
[Ambient sound]

10
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:20.000
[Garden]

11
00:00:18.178 --> 00:00:29.808
[Opera orchestra plays]

12
00:00:18.275 --> 00:00:23.907
Chorus (singing): He said that he stole a hairpin because he was greedy for gold,

13
00:00:29.808 --> 00:00:46.408
[Opera orchestra plays]

14
00:00:46.408 --> 00:01:03.118
[Opera orchestra plays]

15
00:00:47.350 --> 00:00:52.975
and quietly waited outside the garden for Xuechun.

16
00:00:53.375 --> 00:00:58.950
He clapped his hands three times so that the gate would open,

17
00:01:03.118 --> 00:01:21.018
[Opera orchestra plays]

18
00:01:21.018 --> 00:01:29.178
[Opera orchestra plays]

19
00:01:28.175 --> 00:01:33.825
and he could exchange the hairpin for money without any hindrance.

20
00:01:31.918 --> 00:01:34.918
[Opera orchestra plays]

21
00:01:33.825 --> 00:01:35.500
Xuechun: Mr. Lin,

22
00:01:37.478 --> 00:01:43.688
[Opera orchestra plays]

23
00:01:39.550 --> 00:01:40.625
Mr. Lin,

24
00:01:40.950 --> 00:01:43.350
you must not let my lady’s kindness go to waste.

25
00:01:44.650 --> 00:01:45.875
It's getting late,

26
00:01:44.828 --> 00:01:47.388
[Opera orchestra plays]

27
00:01:46.075 --> 00:01:46.850
please go back.

28
00:01:47.888 --> 00:01:52.288
[Opera orchestra plays]

29
00:01:50.550 --> 00:01:54.225
Chorus (singing): Flustered, legs trembling,

30
00:01:53.308 --> 00:01:54.858
[Opera orchestra plays]

31
00:01:54.225 --> 00:01:56.100
he fell to the ground and ruined his plan.

32
00:01:55.708 --> 00:01:56.518
[Opera orchestra plays]

33
00:01:56.100 --> 00:01:57.400
Xuechun: Mr. Lin?

34
00:01:58.024 --> 00:01:58.950
Chorus: Xuechun recognized who it was and shouted loudly.

35
00:01:58.558 --> 00:02:00.678
[Opera orchestra plays]

36
00:01:58.950 --> 00:01:59.700
Ah, it’s you!

37
00:02:00.299 --> 00:02:01.549
Zhang Peizan: Don't shout.

38
00:02:03.050 --> 00:02:04.778
If you shout, I will kill you.

39
00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:08.525
Chorus (singing): One mistake of his caused her soul to travel to the underworld.

40
00:02:06.848 --> 00:02:14.628
[Opera orchestra plays]

41
00:02:08.525 --> 00:02:13.375
Xuechun: Help! Help! Help!

42
00:02:14.628 --> 00:02:15.578
[Sound effect: Gasp]

43
00:02:15.578 --> 00:02:16.825
[Court]

44
00:02:16.825 --> 00:02:18.975
Zhang Peizan: Just when I managed to hide the knife and the gold,

45
00:02:19.525 --> 00:02:20.800
I saw Lin coming over.

46
00:02:23.925 --> 00:02:25.475
So, he became my scapegoat!
